{"id": 1191, "genre": 1001, "title": "你听闻过哪些关于“老”的陈词滥调？", "description": "“30岁了就不能再看动画片”、“高达是小孩子玩的”......这些陈腐的规定，你听过哪些？（题图来自：CHRIS SASAKI）", "record_count": 2554, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160830003339FtK0endsbx8iSGO1.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-09-03T17:00:47Z", "options": [{"id": 117760, "content": "你都多大了还看动画片（ps:谢谢，那叫动漫好嘛，不懂闭嘴）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 765117}, {"id": 113157, "content": "都是为你好", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688519}, {"id": 113159, "content": "啧啧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2337}, {"id": 115210, "content": "阿姨", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 755595}, {"id": 113163, "content": "我就大你2岁，两个小孩都上小学了", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 694623}, {"id": 113165, "content": "这么大了，休息做点正事，别打游戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 745782}, {"id": 113166, "content": "点点滴滴仿佛都反反复复滴滴答答滴滴答答滴滴答答反反复复反反复复滴滴答答滴滴答答滴滴答答滴滴答答纷纷发的反复反反复复反反复复反反复复人点点滴滴点点滴滴仿佛奋斗的方法", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 728473}, {"id": 113167, "content": "什么时候带个男朋友回来，你都多大了今年……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 275406}, {"id": 113423, "content": "胡明明敏敏明明明明明明哦红米你明明你明明", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 728267}, {"id": 113168, "content": "画画能挣钱吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 738210}, {"id": 113169, "content": "你去找98年的那个老女人去吧。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 745909}, {"id": 113426, "content": "都30来岁了还在玩电动玩具，小心嫁不出去啊！", "image": "img/option/option/20160905164923LCZUayp8XFJ1KVSb", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747016}, {"id": 113171, "content": "一把年纪了，还没有男朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693337}, {"id": 113172, "content": "都25了，不要瞎折腾，尝试些不靠谱的东西，你原来那份工作不是挺好么……", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 583289}, {"id": 113173, "content": "别玩儿火，玩儿火尿炕。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713394}, {"id": 113174, "content": "你以后就知道了………", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 745947}, {"id": 113175, "content": "我像你这么大的时候早就怎么怎么治了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 744171}, {"id": 113177, "content": "是该有份事业了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 739705}, {"id": 113178, "content": "还看漫画", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 289971}, {"id": 113179, "content": "…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 745963}, {"id": 113180, "content": "你都多大的人了，还看动画片？（我… 老子就不爱看肥皂剧咋地了", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 564967}, {"id": 113181, "content": "都不想打扮了，真老了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 168948}, {"id": 113182, "content": "年纪要对外用周岁了", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 737679}, {"id": 113183, "content": "25岁了怎么还不生孩子？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 655274}, {"id": 113184, "content": "老娘我……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 392307}, {"id": 113185, "content": "看看别人家小孩，你看看你在看什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 675350}, {"id": 113186, "content": "你以后不好好读书就去拉板车吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 675350}, {"id": 113187, "content": "阿姨好?", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 742663}, {"id": 113188, "content": "涛涛，今晚回家吃饭吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 708407}, {"id": 113189, "content": "不听老人言 吃亏在眼前", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668103}, {"id": 113191, "content": "女人生孩子才完整，该生孩子了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 728511}, {"id": 113192, "content": "这么大了还吃屎", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 738759}, {"id": 114728, "content": "父母说 你多大都是我的孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 748386}, {"id": 113203, "content": "男生就应该做男生该做的事\n女生就该有个女生的样子！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684030}, {"id": 113204, "content": "快三十了 还一事无成", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 746066}, {"id": 113207, "content": "我爸说拼图是小孩玩的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 728355}, {"id": 113208, "content": "大人说话小孩子不要插嘴", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 510108}, {"id": 134714, "content": "都二十四五岁了，还不结婚生孩子，在我们那个年代，像你这种年龄的，好命的都做人母亲了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 836717}, {"id": 113211, "content": "不是我说你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 532125}, {"id": 113213, "content": "老司机", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141957}, {"id": 113215, "content": "什么，你现在还学习，上老年大学吧？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 584803}, {"id": 113217, "content": "女孩子早点找个人嫁出去就行了，还搞什么事业？将来黄脸婆就没人要咯。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 646869}, {"id": 113218, "content": "我吃的盐并吃的你米都多，我走的桥比你走的路都多。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 738934}, {"id": 113219, "content": "好好学习吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 682779}, {"id": 113220, "content": "儿子长大，我在变老", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692609}, {"id": 113222, "content": "都奔三的人了，还没女朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664575}, {"id": 182599, "content": "我看你是嫁不出去了，没人要了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978742}, {"id": 113225, "content": "多大了还玩游戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1057851}, {"id": 114761, "content": "每个人都有童真现实的时候 时而幼稚时而稳重 爱好各有千秋 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753762}, {"id": 113228, "content": "人人都是产品经理?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 223140}]}